{"title":"矿山的歌","authors":["邓平","马天洪","郝来宝","高志勇","蓝田"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是风镐手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碛头面就是地下的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤块在风镐下团团飞旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一朵朵黑色牡丹开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风镐唱着钢铁般的歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座煤山被赶出地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风镐手把温暖送往人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们有一双非凡的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里有一支神奇的赶山鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风钻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风钻风钻，真正能干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天黑夜，都在叫唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起腰杆，不断向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他同岩石，一场大战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻进岩心，挖出煤炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送进高炉，把铁来炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马天洪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工好，矿工好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工下井去挖宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把宝送给高炉吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉咧嘴哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝来宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采煤颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下神来地下神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿风镐采煤层；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风镐钻得突突叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤层让路吐烟云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灰尘起、烟云翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下神在地里钻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来时穿的蓝衣裤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去时变成黑衣衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下神来地下神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善歌善舞样样能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇、摆、俯、仰舞姿好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?、咘、嘟、突奏和声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演员歌舞器乐伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工歌舞伴煤层；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤层歌舞山摇动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献出地下乌金城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高志勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖穿地球就靠我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰隆隆，烟雾蒙蒙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤石飞滚，地塌山崩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石坚硬，就怕决心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天一尺，今天百寸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼打得深，炮轰得准；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石门大开，我们前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要采乌金，谁打先锋？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖穿地球，就靠我们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝田"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}